data.name: toolStripMenuItem2.Text
data.value: Enter Earned and Attempted credits or expected ones in CGPA table, Similarly enter the grades(like A-, a- or f) or grade points(3.67) in grades table for SGPA. Leave the extra semesters, courses or any box you dont need empty or as it is.

data.name: dontPressTheEnterKeyWhileUsingTheAppIfYouFoundAnErrorAfterPressingEnterKeyPressTheResetAllButtonOrRestartTheApplicationToolStripMenuItem.Text
data.value: Dont press the enter key while using the app. If you find an error after pressing enter key press the continue button and if that doesn't help you press the reset all button or restart the application.
